2626:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         requires a timer reset to avoid unexpected direction
2627:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *         due to DIR bit readonly in center aligned mode.
